descriptionHtml:
This is a .jslot preset file for RaceMenu 3

Mods used: Apachii Hair for Males

[b]Installation:[/b]

Place file in Skyrim -> Data -> SKSE -> Plugins -> CharGen -> Presets

[b]How to use:[/b]

1) Select Nord as race
2) Go to the preset tab and load preset (F9 usually) legolas

If you are using this on an old character type showracemenu in the console and follow the steps mentioned above

Also available in my [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/61189/]Ixum's Boys[/url] save collection
